article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Jack Forrest had 24 points in Bucknell's 71-63 win against Navy on Wednesday night. Forrest added seven rebounds for the Bison (7-13, 4-3 Patriot League). Noah Williamson scored 14 points while going 5 of 9 and 4 of 4 from the free throw line. Josh Adoh shot 3 for 5, including 3 for 3 from beyond the arc to finish with 10 points. The Midshipmen (8-10, 4-3) were led by Austin Benigni, who recorded 22 points and four assists. Mac MacDonald added 12 points for Navy and Donovan Draper finished with 11 points and 11 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
